{
  "stem": "8892.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I would stay outside at the gate and just, you know, play around with the ball and casually-- I was trained to just, you know, if I was suspicious, noticed somebody wants to come in our gate, I'd give them some kind of a signal.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "While my father, in the back, in the barn doing this with the-- with the-- the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's when I started to learn what fear is, because we really lived in fear.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But my father didn't want to give in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He didn't want to give in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He just felt that-- I mean, how much chicken and how much goose can you eat, and he had to do it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he risked-- this went on for about three years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he really risked our life and-- you know, as kids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that-- that's what constantly stays in my mind, how-- how really, he just didn't care.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I guess even if they would have arrested him at that point, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But he had to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He felt that because it was just so cruel for him to work seven days-- six, not seven days-- actually five days in a butcher shop, serve them their meat, and he deprived the children, of us and all the Jews, from a piece of calf or a piece of a lamb meat.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all we had, legally, was chicken and goose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Turkey was very rare there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So actually we lived on chicken and goose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was like three, four years going on before then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he just couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he says he doesn't care.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He risked it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First the rabbi was against it, because it wasn't kosher enough, because he did it-- he did it in a barn.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
